<div dir="ltr">Murali,<div><br></div><div>I typically configure with </div><div>   CC=clang CXX=clang++</div><div>on the configure command line.</div><div>Editing of the files generated by configure (such as the Makefile) is not advisable.</div><div><br></div><div>-Paul</div></div><div class="gmail_extra"><br><div class="gmail_quote">On Mon, Jul 18, 2016 at 1:06 PM, Emani, Murali <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:emani1@llnl.gov" target="_blank">emani1@llnl.gov</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br><blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex">



